Thumbnail generator using CLI mtn (https://gitlab.com/movie_thumbnailer/mtn).

Aplication focuses on quick thumbnails-grid creating using drag&drop.

Features:
    - drag&drop files and directories
    - instant image making in background
    - showing image and output log
    - settings dialog for mtn switches


----------
Get source
----------
git clone https://gitlab.com/movie_thumbnailer/qmtn.git qmtn


-----
Build
-----
qmake-qt5 qmtn/mtngui.pro
make -j 4


-------
Install
-------
su -c 'make install'
